TDD specific addition

Time period during which channel information is valid.
Indicates that the maximum time during which the measurement channel information is valid.
0: invalid; 1: 10ms; 2:20ms; 3:50ms; 4:100ms; 5:200ms; 6:500ms; 7:1000ms; 8:1500ms; 9:2000ms; 10: infinite;
